"  Sauce:","1 teaspoon vegetable oil","3/4 cup chopped Vidalia or other sweet onion","2  garlic cloves, minced","1 1/2 cups peach nectar","3 tablespoons brown sugar","2 tablespoons cider vinegar","3 tablespoons bourbon","2 tablespoons ketchup","1 1/2 teaspoons Worcestershire sauce","1/2 teaspoon crushed red pepper","1 tablespoon fresh lime juice","  Steak:","1 tablespoon brown sugar","1 1/4 teaspoons garlic powder","1 1/4 teaspoons ground cumin","1 teaspoon salt","1 teaspoon ground coriander","1 teaspoon paprika","3/4 teaspoon dry mustard","3/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","2  (1-pound) flank steaks, trimmed","  Cooking spray"